<div class="aboutme">
  {/*<Image src={myImage} alt="an image of me" layout="fixed" height={600} class="aboutme-image"/> */}
  

  <div class="aboutme-text">
    <h1>Bryce Hill</h1>

    <p>
      I was an intern at <a title="Not the Fortnite people!" href="https://www.epic.com">Epic</a> this summer, working 
      with .NET and React on insurance related applications in <a href="https://www.mychart.org">MyChart</a>. 

    </p>

    <p>
      I am currently studying Computer Science at Purdue University, focusing on distributed systems and networking. 
      I'm interested in cloud and infrastructure, and I am currently working towards getting various Azure certifications.
    </p>

    <p>
      Outside of work I enjoy listening/making music, lifting heavy objects,
      and reading.
    </p>

    <Links />
  </div>
</div>
